<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5450442&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781512" alt="Ylumwlne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5450442)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;">Ylumwlne</a></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>“我们为了看到光芒</em></p>
